      "rationale": "Nonlinear quasi-static analysis uses full Newton-Raphson with automatic load stepping. Convergence monitored via force and displacement residual norms; all analyses converged within 12 load increments with residuals below 1e-8. Time-step sensitivity study confirmed QoI insensitivity to load increment size over a 4x range. Double-precision arithmetic used throughout; round-off error estimated at <0.001% of QoI magnitude.",
