      "rationale": "Continuum mechanics framework with J2 plasticity (isotropic hardening) selected for Ti-6Al-4V based on published literature and coupon-level validation. Contact between screw and rod modeled using augmented Lagrangian formulation with measured friction coefficient. UHMWPE block represented as linear elastic with measured modulus. Geometric nonlinearity (large deformation) enabled. Model form uncertainty estimated by comparing J2 plasticity against a crystal plasticity surrogate on three representative specimens; mean QoI difference 1.2%, within model form uncertainty budget.",
