      "rationale": "N=11 production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories (Lab 1: n=6, Lab 2: n=5). Specimens sourced from three manufacturing lots to capture lot-to-lot variability. Dimensional inspection confirmed all specimens within drawing tolerance. Specimen traceability maintained via serialization. Inter-laboratory reproducibility assessed; coefficient of variation for stiffness 3.2%, within the pre-specified 5% threshold.",
