      "rationale": "Testing conducted per ASTM F1717-21 with calibrated load frames (NIST-traceable calibration, <0.5% load error). Displacement rate 10 mm/min; temperature 23±1°C; relative humidity 48–52%. Both laboratories used identical fixture geometry verified against F1717 drawings. Load cell and displacement transducer calibration records documented. Environmental conditions logged continuously during testing. Two test conditions explored: standard F1717 offset (50 mm) and a supplementary 40 mm offset run at Lab 1 (n=3) to assess offset sensitivity; primary analysis uses 50 mm offset per standard.",
