      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison of three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) using the ASME V&V 40 validation metric E/uval for all N=11 specimens. All E/uval ratios below 1.96 (stiffness: 0.38; yield force: 0.52; force at 40 mm: 0.44). Relative differences all below 2% (well within the pre-specified 10% acceptance bound). Graphical comparison of full load-displacement curves confirms shape fidelity. Residual analysis shows no systematic bias (Shapiro-Wilk p=0.31 for normality; Durbin-Watson d=1.94 for independence).",
