      "rationale": "Validation activities directly replicate the COU: the same non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw geometry, the same ASTM F1717 loading protocol, and the same QoIs are used in both the validation study and the intended regulatory submission. The FEA model is applied to the identical device design and loading scenario as the COU without extrapolation. The two-laboratory experimental design provides independent confirmation of experimental reproducibility, further strengthening the relevance of the validation evidence base to the submission COU.",
